Title: An Act Changing the Name of Andagaw Elementary School Located in the Municipality of Kalibo, Province of Aklan, to Honorable Juan M. Reyes Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 736
An Act Changing the Name of Andagaw Elementary School Located in the Municipality of Kalibo, Province of Aklan, to Honorable Juan M. Reyes Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Andagaw Elementary School located in the Municipality of Kalibo, Province of Aklan, is hereby changed to Honorable Juan M. Reyes Memorial Elementary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
